<div class="home-page-block-1">
  <div class='homepage-text'>
    <h1 class="h1-homepage">Need some career advice?</h1>
    <h4>We got you.</h4>
    <p>Join us so we can connect you with an experienced
    mentor in any industry. These mentors have
    volunteered to guide and help you in having a
    pleasant and healthy career.</p>
    <% unless user_signed_in? %>
    <div>
      <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class:"btn btn-flat"  %>
    </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div>
    <%= image_tag "homepage-Illustrations-1.png", alt: "mentoree image", height: 400 %>
  </div>

</div></div> <!-- Closing application.html.erb container -->


<div class="white-background-home"><div class="container">   <!-- Opening application.html.erb container -->

  <div id="about" class="home-page-block-2">
    <div class='homepage-text'>
      <h1 class="h1-homepage">Who are we?</h1>
      <p>Mentoree has been created to help any of us create a
      healthy and enjoyable career oriented life. All around us
      millennials seem to be struggling with their career choices
      and we believe it's because we are not motivated to stop and ask
      for guidance every now and then. Mentoree brings together a community
      of experienced mentors and connects them to anyone looking for career
      guidance and advice. in their particular field.
      Sign up to learn more about us!</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <%= image_tag "homepage-Illustrations-2.png", alt: "mentoree image", height: 400 %>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

